Wed Apr 29 15:01:43 UTC 2026 - Christian Goll <cgoll@suse.com>

- Update to 1.19.0 (from 0.23.0)
  * Major changes since 0.23.0:
    - Migrated to microgenerator (v1.0.0)
    - Default to Stackdriver Trace V2 API
    - Added support for REST transport and mTLS
    - Added async context manager support
    - Added API key authentication support
    - Self-signed JWT flow for service accounts
    - Native namespace package compatibility
  * Changes in 1.19.0:
    - Allow Protobuf 7.x
    - Improve type checking
  * Breaking changes from 0.x series:
    - Removed span_path resource helper (v0.24.0)
    - Minimum Python version increased from 3.6 to 3.9
    - Changed to microgenerator with new API surface
- Download source via service
- Fix dependencies
- Add pytest-asyncio for tests

